## 4. Spec 驱动开发三件套工作流

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 用户/PM
    participant SP as spec-proposal
    participant SD as spec-design
    participant ST as spec-tasks
    participant KR as knowledge-recall
    participant KB as 知识库
    participant CODE as 代码库

    Note over U,CODE: === Phase 1: 需求提案 (spec-proposal) ===
    U->>SP: PRD / 需求描述
    SP->>KB: 加载 constitution.md (最高约束)
    SP->>KR: 知识召回 (关键词 + 路径)
    KR-->>SP: 命中知识点 + 模块文档
    SP->>CODE: grep/glob 影响分析
    SP->>CODE: 疑问点自证 (先自证后求证)
    SP-->>SP: ✅ 代码确认 / ⚠️ 需确认
    SP->>U: AskUserQuestion (仅 ⚠️ 级)
    U-->>SP: 确认
    SP->>KB: 保存 proposal.md
    SP->>KB: 沉淀新知识 (Phase 5.5)

    Note over U,CODE: === Phase 2: 技术方案 (spec-design) ===
    U->>SD: 开始设计
    SD->>KB: 读取 proposal.md + constitution.md
    SD->>CODE: 正向调用链: UI→Presenter→SDK→Connection→Protocol
    SD->>CODE: 反向调用链: Protocol→Event→VM→UI
    SD-->>SD: 标注 ✅/⚠️ + 修改策略
    SD->>SD: 冲突风险标注 (方案A/B)
    SD->>SD: Constitution 逐项检查
    SD->>U: AskUserQuestion (仅 ⚠️ 级决策)
    SD->>KB: 保存 design.md
    SD->>KB: 沉淀调用链新认知

    Note over U,CODE: === Phase 3: 任务拆解 (spec-tasks) ===
    U->>ST: 开始拆解
    ST->>KB: 读取 design.md + proposal.md
    ST->>CODE: 任务拆解 (文件路径级)
    ST->>CODE: 路径验证 (glob/grep)
    ST->>CODE: 隐含依赖检测
    Note over ST: Protocol实现类 / Notification同步 /<br/>接口移除影响 / 替代API检测
    ST->>ST: 约束注入 (submodule/OC-Swift/车型)
    ST->>KB: 保存 tasks.md
    ST->>U: TodoWrite 创建跟踪项
    Note over ST: 末尾预置: post-task-review 提醒
```

